ass="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/ot/lev/18.html?verse=4#p4" href="/scriptures/ot/lev/18.4?lang=spa#p4">Levítico 18:4</a>;<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.html?verse=5-12#p5" href="/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.5-12?lang=spa#p5"> 2 Nefi 31:5–12</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.html?verse=12-16#p12" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.12-16?lang=spa#p12">Doctrina y Convenios 1:12–16</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.html?verse=4#p4" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.4?lang=spa#p4">136:4</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.html?verse=3-4#p3" href="/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.3-4?lang=spa#p3">Artículos de Fe 1:3–4</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note12-"><span class="label">12. </span><p data-aid="138781048" id="note12_p1">Véanse <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.html?verse=20-21#p20" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.20-21?lang=spa#p20">Doctrina y Convenios 84:20–21</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.html?verse=9#p9" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.9?lang=spa#p9">110:9</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note13-"><span class="label">13. </span><p data-aid="138781054" id="note13_p1">Véanse <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/ot/josh/3.html?verse=5#p5" href="/scriptures/ot/josh/3.5?lang=spa#p5">Josué 3:5</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.html?verse=16#p16" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.16?lang=spa#p16">Doctrina y Convenios 43:16</a>; véase también <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/john/17.html?verse=19#p19" href="/scriptures/nt/john/17.19?lang=spa#p19">Juan 17:19</a>. El Salvador se sacrificó para tener el poder de bendecirnos